# Project Architecture

- Layered Architecture:
  - Controller: src/main/java/com/example/demo/controller
  - Service: src/main/java/com/example/demo/service
  - Repository: src/main/java/com/example/demo/mapper
  - Model: src/main/java/com/example/demo/model
  - Configuration: src/main/java/com/example/demo/config
  - Mapstruct Converter: src/main/java/com/example/demo/converter
  - DTO: src/main/java/com/example/demo/dto
  - Exception Handling: src/main/java/com/example/demo/exceptions
  - Utility Classes: src/main/java/com/example/demo/utils
  - Management Database Migrations use Liquibase: src/main/resources/db/changelog
- Database ORM: Mybatis Plus 3.5.14

